     <div type="to_the_reader">
   <pb facs="1"/>
   <head>The Author to the Reader.</head>
   <p>I Beseech you to peruse this little Booke of my owne making: imprinted at my own cost &amp; charges. Which I humbly intreat you to ac<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>cept at my hands: not weighing the worth, but re<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>specting my good will. And deale therein (in your <hi>ver<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>tuous disposition, and Christian loue and charity</hi>) as God shall moue your minde.</p>
   <closer>
      <signed>
         <hi>I. A.</hi> Minister and Prea<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>cher of Gods Word.</signed>
   </closer>
</div>
